{"type":"message","id":"5efef6b1","parentId":"dcf397af","timestamp":"2026-03-27T23:00:00.359Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:10a19bb7-7afb-4b24-8478-62555b540c2d daily-ping-telegram] Send daily ping to Telegram with this EXACT format:\n\n🌅 Daily Ping — {DAY}, {MMM} {DD}, {YYYY}\n\n💰 Bitcoin\n• Price: ${BTC_PRICE} USD\n• 24h: {BTC_CHANGE}% {TREND}\n\n📊 Tech Stocks\n• NVDA: ${PRICE} ({CHANGE}%) {TREND}\n• MSFT: ${PRICE} ({CHANGE}%) {TREND}\n• GOOGL: ${PRICE} ({CHANGE}%) {TREND}\n• INTC: ${PRICE} ({CHANGE}%) {TREND}\n• META: ${PRICE} ({CHANGE}%) {TREND}\n• AMD: ${PRICE} ({CHANGE}%) {TREND}\n\n📊 Market: S&P {SPX}, Nasdaq {NDX} — {BRIEF_COMMENTARY}\n\n🚀 Trending GitHub Repos (Created Since 2025)\n1. {repo} ⭐ {stars}K\n... (top 10)\n\n— ⏰ {HH}:{MM} SGT | Data: CoinGecko, Yahoo Finance, GitHub API\n\nFetch fresh data using:\n- Bitcoin: CoinGecko API (price + 24h change)\n- Stocks: Yahoo Finance (NVDA, MSFT, GOOGL, INTC, META, AMD)\n- Indices: S&P 500 and NasdaqComposite\n- GitHub: top 10 repos created since 2025, sorted by stars\n\nSend to Telegram target 1087368827 using the message tool.\nCurrent time: Saturday, March 28th, 2026 — 7:00 AM (Asia/Singapore) / 2026-03-27 23:00 UTC"}],"timestamp":1774652400358}}
{"type":"message","id":"eb634ba2","parentId":"5efef6b1","timestamp":"2026-03-27T23:03:13.253Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":" The user wants me to send a daily ping to Telegram with specific data. I need to:\n1. Fetch Bitcoin price and 24h change from CoinGecko API\n2. Fetch stock prices for NVDA, MSFT, GOOGL, INTC, META, AMD from Yahoo Finance\n3. Fetch S&P 500 and Nasdaq indices\n4. Fetch top 10 trending GitHub repos created since 2025, sorted by stars\n5. Format everything according to the exact template provided\n6. Send to Telegram target 1087368827\n\nLet me start by fetching the data from these APIs. I'll use web_search or web_fetch to get this information.\n\nActually, for crypto prices, CoinGecko API is free and doesn't require auth for basic endpoints. For stocks, Yahoo Finance has an API I can use. For GitHub, the search API.\n\nLet me make","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":" I'll fetch the fresh data and send your daily ping. Getting Bitcoin from CoinGecko, stocks from Yahoo Finance, and trending"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"functions.web_fetch:0","name":"web_fetch","arguments":{"url":"https://api.coingecko.com/api/v3/simple/price?ids=bitcoin&vs_currencies=usd&include_24hr_change=true"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"functions.web_fetch:1","name":"web_fetch","arguments":{"url":"https://query1.finance.yahoo.com/v8/finance/chart/NVDA,MSFT,GOOGL,INTC,META,AMD,^GSPC,^IXIC?interval=1d&range=1d"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"functions.web_fetch:2","name":"web_fetch","arguments":{"url":"https://api.github.com/search/repositories?q=created:>2025-01-01&sort=stars&order=desc&per_page=10"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"nvidia","model":"moonshotai/kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":17138,"output":366,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":17504,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774652400359,"responseId":"chatcmpl-8eb2279b67ca60d5"}}
